<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">近日，国家文物局、教育部办公厅公布了以革命文物为主题的“大思政课”优质资源项目名单，<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">确定了10个示范项目、100个精品项目。</span></span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 37.3333px; color: black !important;">我校与井冈山革命博物馆联合报送的“八角楼——实事求是闯新路”视频微课入选新媒体产品类项目。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18.6667px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 37.3333px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">据悉，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">以革命文物为主题的“大思政课”优质资源建设推广工作由国家文物局、教育部联合开展，</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28pt;">江西省一共5个项目入选（南昌大学、江西师范大学、赣南师范大学、豫章师范学院和江西软件职业技术大学各入选1个项目</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18.6667px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 37.3333px;">），<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">我校是全国唯一的职业本科高校获得此项殊荣。</span></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-28%2014%3A40%3A33a70f9adf0498beb8b1fb786de89dfd3.jpg?Expires=2016513633&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=m3QlUMRG6%2FnIo4ta%2BokajaL2hjs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="617" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">国家文物局、教育部两部门表示，要以示范项目和精品项目为引导，进一步聚焦主题，依据不同受众着力开发一批契合教学目标的思政课程，着力打造一批“纪念馆里的思政课”“行走的思政课”品牌，切实推动不同学段学生走进场馆开展学习实践，充分发挥革命文物铸魂育人作用。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-28%2014%3A53%3A24%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20231128145236.png?Expires=2016514404&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=bp2ebs01Yui35m3uNnLoX%2B7Oxoc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="485" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">学校将以此为契机，持续深入学习贯彻习近平总书记关于革命文物工作和</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“大思政课”的重要指示批示精神，聚焦立德树人根本任务，用好革命文物资源，充分发挥革命文物、革命文化在爱国主义教育和“大思政课”建设工作中的作用，努力推进革命文物融入思政教育一体化建设。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>